                  "revisionId": 2790945,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The detonation area is a sphere centered on the point where Hallowed Ground was created, inheriting the Hallowed Ground's radius. It is able to hit enemies that are not affected by Hallowed Ground, as long as they are in Hallowed Eruption's area."
